---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — Bebop">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
      <a href="/" class="text-primary hover:underline text-sm">&larr; Back to home</a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold font-serif mt-6 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-6 text-foreground leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using Bebop, you agree to be bound by these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the service.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Account & Access</h2>
        <p>Bebop is currently in early access. Access is granted through invite codes and the waitlist. You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account credentials and for all activity under your account.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p>You agree to use Bebop only for lawful purposes. You may not use the platform to distribute spam, malware, or content that violates the rights of others. We reserve the right to suspend accounts that violate these terms.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Your Content</h2>
        <p>You retain ownership of all content you create and publish through Bebop. We do not claim any intellectual property rights over your content. By using the platform, you grant us a limited license to store and transmit your content as necessary to operate the service.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Bebop is provided "as is" during early access. We make no warranties regarding uptime, data preservation, or fitness for a particular purpose. To the maximum extent permitted by law, Bebop and its contributors shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the service.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms as the platform evolves. We will notify registered users of significant changes via email. Continued use of Bebop after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@bebopcms.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@bebopcms.com</a>.</p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />
        <p class="text-sm text-muted italic">This is a placeholder terms of service. Full terms will be published before Bebop exits early access.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
